data.description: Welcome to Long View Estates, a quiet little oasis situated in the growing little city of Loris. This home has been completely updated and has so much to offer with 4 Bedrooms, 2 full baths, a spacious split floor plan, a formal dining room with beautiful built in cabinets, a family room and living room, it has an open kitchen with tons of cabinet space, a large laundry room and 1800 heated sqft situated on almost one acre. The paint & flooring has been updated throughout, it has a new roof in 2019, new under skirting in 2020, new HVAC in 2021, new water heater in 2021, brand new propane fireplace insert, new flooring in the master bath & laundry room, a well for irrigation & city water to the house. This home is turn key ready for you!
